                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Tripudio Elementale</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Infligge 1 </span><span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">DAN da Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">, evoca 1 </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">Tengu Juurai: Ammassatempesta</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.<br></span></p>",
